PrecisAuthority for the Correctional Service of Canada to enter into an EXCHANGE OF SERVICES AGREEMENT with the Government of NUNAVUT concerning the transfer and temporary detention of offenders in federal or territorial penal institutions, the provision of community assessment services and the supervision of parolees, and the financial arrangements to be made in respect thereof.
Attachments
precis:
Authority for the Correctional Service of Canada to enter into an EXCHANGE
OF SERVICES AGREEMENT with the Government of NUNAVUT concerning the
transfer and temporary detention of offenders in federal or territorial
penal institutions, the provision of community assessment services and
the supervision of parolees, and the financial arrangements to be made in
respect thereof.
